data.description: Welcome to a dream-home opportunity that offers you not just a house, but a lifestyle. Situated with exclusive access to Canyon Lake, this beloved property comes with two private parks to the lakefront and its own private cove, truly a paradise of peace and tranquility! This is an incredible opportunity to own a rare opportunity in Canyon Lake. A spacious single-story layout, this home features 3 nice-sized bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. With plenty of natural light flowing throughout the home's open and airy layout, it gives a warmth that's hard to find elsewhere. Cook up a storm in the large kitchen, big enough for all your culinary needs. And the separate dining room is the perfect setting to enjoy those delicious meals with your loved ones. Whether you're working from home or homeschooling, the dedicated office/study area provides a quiet and comfortable space to focus and be productive. One of the key features of this property is its impressive oversized lot. Nestled on over half an acre, it offers unparalleled space for outdoor activities or future expansion. For the outdoor adventurer or hobbyist, the property provides the luxury of a large garage/barn, big enough to store a boat or any other recreational vehicle. Additionally, there's an RV parking area with dedicated RV hookups-making it a perfect fit for road trip enthusiasts. Imagine owning a property that harmoniously blends comfort, convenience and charm home offers just that. Don't wait up, schedule your visit today!
